Cell["\<\
Note that the density operator does not consist purely of z-terms, but also \
double and triple products of z-operators. This is correct. The matrix \
representation of this operator shows that all spins are in the |\[Alpha]\
\[Alpha]\[Alpha]> state:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.681107906367447*^9, 
  3.681107953921165*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"823b1144-8106-4a1b-b82e-\
