Cell["\<\
The singlet polarization level is modulated since the selective rf field on \
just one of the coupled spins converts singlet population into triplet \
population, and back again.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.681111114170404*^9, 
  3.681111148314204*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ce3a73dd-9226-43ad-bfed-\
967981c06f26"]
